definition_zib: Root concept of the Payer information model. This root concept contains all data elements of the Payer information model.
definition_xtehr: EHDS refined base model for Coverage

definition_zib: Type of insurance policy. Codes as returned in the Check for Right to Insurance
short_xtehr: Type of coverage: social program, medical plan, accident coverage (workers compensation, auto), group health or payment by an individual or organisation.
definition_xtehr: Type of coverage: social program, medical plan, accident coverage (workers compensation, auto), group health or payment by an individual or organisation.

short_xtehr: Patient who benefits from the insurance coverage when products and/or services are provided.
definition_xtehr: Patient who benefits from the insurance coverage when products and/or services are provided.

definition_zib: Root concept of the Payer information model. This root concept contains all data elements of the Payer information model.
short_xtehr: Payor including both insurance and non-insurance agreements, such as patient-pay agreements.
definition_xtehr: Payor including both insurance and non-insurance agreements, such as patient-pay agreements.

definition_zib:
Number under which the insured person is registered at the insurance company 
This item maps the ‘Identification number of the card’ on EHIC field 8
short_xtehr: Number or code under which the insured person is registered at the insurance provider.
definition_xtehr: Number or code under which the insured person is registered at the insurance provider.

definition_zib:
Container of the PayerPerson concept. This container contains all data elements of the PayerPerson concept.
In this a person is a natural person or a juridical person, such as an organization, municipality, etc.
Full name of the paying person or organization (legal entity).
Container of the BankInformation concept. This container contains all data elements of the BankInformation concept.
Code indicating the bank and branch. For European countries, this is the organization’s BIC or SWIFT code.
The payer’s bank account number at the listed organization. For European countries, this is the IBAN.
Container of the InsuranceCompany concept. This container contains all data elements of the InsuranceCompany concept.
Container of the Insurance concept. This container contains all data elements of the Insurance concept.

Full, official name of the healthcare insurance company. If the UZOVI number is entered as an identification number, this will be the name as listed in the UZOVI register and the name which is returned in the Check for Right to Insurance (COV).
Unique healthcare insurance company identification (the UZOVI number).
Date from which the insurance policy coverage applies.

Date until which the insurance policy coverage applies. 
This item maps the ‘Expiry date’ on EHIC field 9.
The payer’s telephone number and/or e-mail address.
